		   Xtwitter - twitter client for X

Xtwitter is very tiny twitter client for X Window System.
It'll works on Linux, and other UNIX-like operating systems.

* Project URL
  http://www.cuspy.org/xtwitter/

* Requirements

  X.org
  Imlib2
  libcurl
  glib 2.0
  liboauth
  libjson

* Build

  % ./configure

  % make

* Configration

  % mkdir ~/.xtwitter
  % cat > ~/.xtwitter/config
  user=test
  pass=xxxxxxxx
  ^D

